name: NYDailyNews
text:
Nick Saban, coach of the Crimson Tide, urged Alabamians to wear masks to curb coronavirus.

“All of us want to make sure we play football this fall,” he said. “And to make that happen ... please wear a mask anytime you’re around other people.”
https://t.co/SaAX1k6qtp

name: NYDailyNews
text:
Doctors put a stent in Thomas Marshall two months ago hoping to buy time for the pandemic to pass before scheduling a heart surgery.

It didn’t.

The heart surgery team at Mount Sinai had to get back to business after weeks of dedicated coronavirus care.
https://t.co/dWVOTKiW7t

The Florida-based company was working to reach a deal with lenders, but the efforts fell through.

A portion of the proceeds will go to TAPS, an organization providing resources to military survivors.

name: NYDailyNews
text:
One America News Network’s defamation suit against Rachel Maddow was tossed.

In dismissing the suit, U.S. Judge Cynthia Bashant ruled that Maddow was offering an opinion based on an accurate article summation when she called OANN "Russian propaganda."
https://t.co/UOv133G7Fy
